PrecisSCHEDULE No. 875 to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS - which establishes a maximum residue limit on the amount of the herbicide "TRIASULFURON" that can be detected on wheat, it being a new selective herbicide providing fall and spring pre-emergent residual control of many broadleaf weeds in spring wheat.

precis:
SCHEDULE No. 875 to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS - which establishes a
maximum residue limit on the amount of the herbicide "TRIASULFURON" that
can be detected on wheat, it being a new selective herbicide providing fall
and spring pre-emergent residual control of many broadleaf weeds in spring
wheat.
